    "longBusinessSummary": "Power Engineering Consulting Joint Stock Company 2 engages in the investigation, planning, design, supervision, and construction management of power source and grid projects in Vietnam. The company offers power engineering consulting services for hydropower and renewable engineering, thermal and nuclear power engineering, transmission and distribution engineering, and survey and construction projects, as well as for power sources and electrical grids. It also provides technical research and application services for power source and network projects; engineering, procurement, and construction general contractor services; mechanical processing and equipment manufacturing services; mechanical manufacture services for energy projects; and construction, operation, and management services for power plants. In addition, the company engages in the design and manufacture of auxiliary systems for power plants; and trading in electricity. Further, it operates a training, research, and development center, as well as a digital capability center; and invests in power plants, including mini-hydropower, solar power, wind power, biomass energy, and gas fueled power plants. The company was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. Power Engineering Consulting Joint Stock Company 2 is a subsidiary of Vietnam Power Group.",
